data.description: Oh, Kale yeah! Everyone loves going green. Your friends will be green with envy, a green that would make the Grinches heart grow 3 times bigger, and a price that won’t make you turn green. This unique home nestled on the side of Sunrise Mountain features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and an in-ground pool with an attached spa. Beautiful Mountain views, plenty of natural light, and all the green that you’re missing by living in the desert.
